Text Summarization using T5 (Hugging Face)
Overview
This repository contains code for performing text summarization using the T5 (Text-To-Text Transfer Transformer) model from Hugging Face Transformers. The implementation uses TensorFlow and Keras for training and inference.

Getting Started
Prerequisites
Make sure you have the required dependencies installed. You can install them using:

bash
Copy code
pip install transformers==4.20.0
pip install keras_nlp==0.3.0
pip install datasets
pip install huggingface-hub
pip install nltk
pip install rouge-score
