Usage
Open the Jupyter Notebook hari_reddy-summarization_using_T5.ipynb using a Jupyter environment.

Run the notebook cell by cell, ensuring that dependencies are installed as mentioned in the first cell.

Follow the instructions and comments in the notebook to understand each step, including loading the dataset, tokenization, model training (uncomment if needed), and summarization.

Customize the code as needed for your specific use case, such as using a different dataset or adjusting hyperparameters.

Dataset
The code utilizes the XSum dataset from EdinburghNLP. You can replace it with your own dataset by modifying the data_path variable in the notebook.
